ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMexico - Mutual Recognition Agreement for Conformity Assessment of Telecommunications Equipment ** RATIFICATION **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the MUTUAL RECOGNITION AGREEMENT FOR CONFORMITY ASSESSMENT OF TELECOMMUNICATIONS EQUIPMENT between Canada and the UNITED MEXICAN STATES.
